			text="In this activity you will review existing sources of information on hazards, disasters, and threats (HDT) your community faces or might face in the future.">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
		<textBlock>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Bold"
			text="Why do this: ">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="&#xD;You may want to share this information with members of the community and include it in a plan or report.">
			</text>
		</textBlock>
