			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="&#xD;- Share what you find with the core team and discuss what other questions you have.">
			</text>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="&#xD;- Consider reaching out to a local university to get assistance with interpreting the data you find.">
